name: Project Uncensored
short_description:
Project Uncensored Will be a small peace of software that you will run on your windows based computers that will allow you to connect to a network that will route your online traffic all a round the World that will better protect your online privacy by never revealing your real IP address to and website or service online

How this software works
This software will work with any browser you have install on your computer so there's no need to change your browser for this to work. This software works by connecting you to our servers then routing your traffic  throw out different nodes on the internet to keep your online activities anonymous secure and private

So all you need to do is run this software on any version of windows from windows XP upto windows 8.1. Click the connect button on the software to connect to our servers ones the connection is successfully connected. All that's left to do now is open the browser you have installed on your computer and enter your blocked URL
